                            <comment id="12799083" author="stack" created="Tue, 12 Jan 2010 05:52:02 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for filing the issue.  This has come up before (Yes it was hbase-1304 that did this).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Put and Delete should have common ancestor and we should add at least a batch Put+Delete to HTable.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Would be grand too if going from a Result to a Put were easier than copying their guts.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
